# {{lb|zh|classical}} to [[decline]], [[diminish]]
# {{n-g|Used in [[onomatopoeia]]s.}}

====Usage notes====
Use {{zh-m|剝}} for peeling something with one's hands, like a tangerine. Use {{zh-m|削}} for peeling something with a [[knife]] or [[peeler]], like a potato.

